# HCP Terraform ingests the whole repo on each VCS run, but the workspace only runs Terraform
# in infra/ — which uploads examples/public-metrics/ to the sample bucket. Ship just those two so
# the ingress archive stays small (the rest is the product: server/, tools/, site/, docs/, …).

# Ignore everything at the repo root, then re-include only what the infra/ run needs.
/*
!/infra
!/examples
/examples/*
!/examples/public-metrics

# The WIF bootstrap is run once by a human, not by the TFC run — keep it out of the archive.
/infra/scripts
